task.summary: Attempting to solve relative path issues and git issues.
Made a new project to fix IDE path issues. Also have sound working with relative path, but it is the path to the out dir instead of resources.
Mostly giving up on getting sound to work in a jar. The jar compiles and plays the game correctly, but without the buzzer. Now going to focus on readme and design document.
Added gitignore and slight readme updates.
Added validation to initializeHand call. Updated readme.
Completely re-designed the board. Uses a canvas. One bug exists where the board will flip if the modulo is off by 1 per prepending the list.
Final commit for the project. Canvas draws the dominos beautifully.
j/k, one more commit. Updated powerpoint and optimized the board grid method.
